OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1784189889
OL,3,CCashpoint scammer caught after using
OL,4,Cown bank card
OL,6,FFelix and Cristian Urcaciu brothers
OL,7,Ffitted 'trap devices' to ATMs to scam
OL,8,Fcustomers out of their cash withdrawals
OL,10,FA thief who fitted trap devices to
OL,11,Fcashpoints across the East Midlands
OL,12,Fhas been caught after police tracked
OL,13,Fhim through his bank card.
OL,15,FFeilx Urcaciu used his card to make
OL,16,Fbalance enquiries as he fitted a metal
OL,17,Fenvelope device to ATM cash dispensers.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
