PN,34702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1784189889
OL,3,CCashpoint scammer caught after using
OL,4,Cown bank card
OL,6,FHe and his brother, Cristian Urcaciu,
OL,7,Fstole at least #25,000 in the scam
OL,8,Fwhere customers assumed the machines
OL,9,Fwere faulty.
OL,11,FNottinghamshire Police analysed CCTV
OL,12,Ffootage of the reportedly faulty
OL,13,Fcashpoints and identified two suspects
OL,14,Fand two vehicles, linking Felix to the
OL,15,Fthefts through his own bank card.
OL,17,FDetectives linked the brothers to
OL,18,Fother offences in Leicester, Leeds,
OL,19,FSheffield, Wakefield, Derbyshire and
OL,20,FScotland.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,348,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1784189889
OL,3,CCashpoint scammer caught after using
OL,4,Cown bank card
OL,6,FOn searching Cristian's home in
OL,7,FBarnsley on 2 August 2023, officers
OL,8,Fdiscovered an improvised workshop in a
OL,9,Fgarage where the trap devices were
OL,10,Fbeing made, as well as a hook device
OL,11,Fused to remove the traps from ATMs.
OL,13,FCristian and another person were
OL,14,Farrested before Felix arrived carrying
OL,15,Fstolen cash from an offence committed
OL,16,Fin Sheffield that morning.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
