FL,348,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1784189889
OL,3,CCashpoint scammer caught after using
OL,4,Cown bank card
OL,6,FCristian pleaded guilty to conspiracy
OL,7,Fto steal and concealing criminal
OL,8,Fproperty, and has been sentenced to 33
OL,9,Fmonths in prison at Nottingham Crown
OL,10,FCourt.
OL,12,FFelix was found guilty in his absence
OL,13,Fof conspiracy to steal, concealing
OL,14,Fcriminal property and possessing
OL,15,Fcriminal property. He has been handed
OL,16,Fa jail term of 40 months.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
