PN,34705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1784189889
OL,3,CCashpoint scammer caught after using
OL,4,Cown bank card
OL,6,FPolice staff investigator, Jodie
OL,7,FMottishaw, said: "This was a
OL,8,Fcalculated and cynical conspiracy that
OL,9,Finvolved the subsequent movement of
OL,10,Fmoney to several bank accounts.
OL,12,F"Ultimately, however, the brothers
OL,13,Fwere undone by their own greed and
OL,14,Fcarelessness."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/5
